e Whitman]] also joined the cast.<ref>{{cite web | last=Kroll | first=Justin | title=\u2018Parenthood\u2019 Star Mae Whitman Joins \u2018Valley Girl\u2019 Musical Remake (EXCLUSIVE) | url=https://variety.com/2017/film/news/mae-whitman-valley-girl-remake-1202409144/ | work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] | date=May 4, 2017 | accessdate=February 16, 2019}}</ref> In June 2017, [[Peyton List (actress, born 1998)|Peyton List]] joined the cast of the film.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2017/06/valley-girl-peyton-list-mgm-1202106616/|title=MGM\u2019s \u2018Valley Girl\u2019 Remake Adds Peyton List|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|date=June 2, 2017|accessdate=February 16, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Release==\nThe film was scheduled to be released on June 29, 2018, however, it was pulled from the schedule, following [[Logan_Paul#2017\u20132018:_Suicide_forest_controversy|controversies surrounding Logan Paul]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/03/logan-paul-valley-girl-release-date-change-1202307858/|title=\u2018Valley Girl\u2019 Remake With Controversial YouTuber Logan Paul Looking For Another Release Date|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=November 1, 2018|accessdate=February 16, 2019}}</ref> It is scheduled to be released on May 8, 2020.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/movies/valley-girl-remake-first-look/|title=Exclusive: Here's a, like, super rad look at the Valley Girl musical remake|website=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|first=Devan|last=Coggan|date=April 15, 2020|accessdate=April 15, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDB title|1266036}}\n\n[[Category:Upcoming films]]\n[[Category:American films]]\n[[Category:American comedy films]]\n[[Category:American romantic comedy films]]\n[[Category:American musical comedy films]]\n[[Category:American film remakes]]\n[[Category:Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer films]]\n[[Category:Films directed by Rachel Lee Goldenberg]]\n", "name_user": "HM2021"